{"tid":1747284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲分化？「五大訴求，缺一不可」保皇黨會支持？","createTime":"2019-11-23T07:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T12:43:53.000Z","uid":229880,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc8af77b1df8a24bcb4cd4bc2cac08796657f040","tid":1747284,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:02:10.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n係呢五個多月嘅社會共識<br />\n<br />\n「民意」係我地所有抗爭者嘅無形後盾，並強化不割蓆嘅其中理據<br />\n<br />\n如果連票數都輸俾保皇黨，仲有無可能講得出民意係我地果邊？<br />\n<br />\n點解仲有班友講得出投保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我睇唔透連登係咪得返五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f447f7ec11e0c5fef0df3744a208e4b5893a1a47","tid":1747284,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:02:20.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"0729be5a429f34b1b6e39fbf00cf78361015aba5","tid":1747284,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"eaf1e2063befa71bcb4a0887a6a5a707e0c12ca6","tid":1747284,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:02:43.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"22358579ed5ab52de11fe02fce2f43347967bd8d","tid":1747284,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:02:53.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"d277b835200cc3c0edeaaba446ab4b83edbc4f83","tid":1747284,"uid":251265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:02:56.000Z","msg":"企圖抹黑民主派，呼籲手足投白票一律視為共諜"},{"pid":"f5374a35c16d78dd3ed4e3a9898323bd232c617c","tid":1747284,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"2a917b42fe231eed1225ff5589b2fcdaa6c6e2f7","tid":1747284,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0